location.fullValue: Corsica Plan, Estates at Hampton Place

data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in North Ridgeville's Waterbury development! This stunning Colonial-style 2-story home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, providing plenty of space for your family to live and grow.

As you enter, you'll be greeted by a grand foyer flanked by formal living and dining rooms. The spacious family room with a cozy fireplace is the perfect place to gather and unwind after a long day. The large kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, a deep under-mount sink, and stainless steel appliances, making meal prep and entertaining a breeze. Enjoy your morning coffee in the bright and airy morning room, overlooking the backyard.

Convenient first-floor laundry, an office, and a half bath complete the main level. Upstairs, you'll find a luxurious master suite with an adjoining sitting room and an en-suite bath with a soaking tub, providing a private retreat for relaxation. Three more bedrooms and a full bath complete the second floor.

This home also features a huge unfinished basement, providing endless possibilities for storage, a home gym, or additional living space. Step outside and enjoy the large yard and deck, perfect for outdoor entertaining and relaxation.

Located in the Waterbury development, you'll have access to 142 acres of open space, a clubhouse facility, swimming pool, miles of walking trails, and several scenic lakes and tot lots. Don't miss your chance to call this beautiful home yours!
